messages.messageBody:
Oh Maisha, I SO understand. We are living with my sis, who is ultra
traditional, until we close on our house. It is very hard tiptoeing
around at night, making sure the kids have their food in the kitchen
and such. Very stressful at times! Hang in there!!!!

Heidi

messages.messageBody:
Hello to everyone! I would like to ask for good vibes and energy sent
to my family please. We are currently displaced and need to get back
on our feet. It's hard to unschool in someone else's house, ya know?
And the pressure to conform is tremendous!!!! I don't get to get on
the internet much, and I need, NEED your support!! So just please
send prayers, reiki, light a candle, do a spell....whatever! So that
we can get our own home and get back to the business of being our
crazy, wonderful, happy, peaceful selves.

Thanks so much
Maisha
Khalfani Family Adventures at Blogger.com
